    "verification_notes": "DC phone (202) 225-1555 confirmed, matching prior unverified value. DC fax (202) 226-0396 from TX State Directory and BillTrack50. babin.house.gov returns 403 to automated fetches; data cross-referenced from txdirectory.com, Texas Tribune directory, BillTrack50, Orange Leader, and MOAA. Four district offices confirmed: Deer Park (main, by appointment), Lumberton, Woodville (Tyler County Courthouse), and Orange (Orange City Hall, relocated 2019). Orange and Lumberton share phone (409) 883-8075 per MOAA source; Orange fax not listed separately. Social media verified via Wikidata, search results, and babin.house.gov footer references: X (@RepBrianBabin), Facebook (RepBrianBabin), Instagram (rep.brianbabin), YouTube (channel UCPVEZgw-VbDRbLV1MRGVQNQ). No Bluesky or Truth Social accounts found. Campaign site babinforcongress.com confirmed via Wikipedia external links. Web contact form at babin.house.gov/contact (zip-code-gated writeyourrep form). Texas Tribune listed a Dayton satellite office (2004 N. Cleveland St.) but this was not corroborated by TX State Directory or other authoritative sources and is omitted pending verification."
  }
